    "body": "The overriding can be done by adding the following style to each `_repr_html_`:\r\n\r\n```\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n  table.dataframe td, table.dataframe th {\r\n    max-width: none;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n```\r\n\r\nOther options could be:\r\n\r\n- see all data on hover\r\n- wrap longer cells"
  },
