    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Another issue is that, IMO, we should keep some kind of wrapping long text in multiple lines, see eg the notebook here: http://nbviewer.jupyter.org/gist/epifanio/e82443b79c24ceb2d59ba49cad9a62d4 (from gitter). \r\nEven if you can use `pd.options.display.max_colwidth` to set it to a really high number eg 1000, this is only useful if the long text is wrapped over multiple lines, and not on one gigantic line (as you would get with current jupyterlab/notebook master.\r\n\r\n"
  },
